    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Comparison Report: COL/COADREAD\"\nauthor: \"Ali Al-Timimi, PhD\"\nformat: html\nparams:\n  data_file: \"C:/Users/drziy/OneDrive/Desktop/Ali/scientific_research_current/global-cancer-complexity/output/global_cancer/RData/comparison_data/comparison_data_col_coadread.rds\"\nexecute:\n  eval: true\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n### COL/COADREAD Overview\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Probes\n> -   **Cancer Category:** carcinomas\n> -   **Chip hu35ksuba**: 1129 filtered probes\n> -   **Chip hu6800**: 286 filtered probes\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](../../resources/plots/probes/col_coadread_probe_counts.png){width=7in}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n#### Summary Assessment\n\n**Overall Complexity & Entropy Assessment**\n\n| Measure | All Filtered Probes | GO MF Terms | KEGG Pathways | HALLMARK Genes |\n|:---|:---|:---|:---|:---|\n| **Complexity** | not available | strong loss (well supported) | strong loss (well supported) | strong loss (moderately supported) |\n| **Shannon Entropy** | not available | strongly chaotic (uncertain) | mildly chaotic (uncertain) | strongly chaotic (moderately supported) |\n| **Spectral Entropy** | not available | no clear change (uncertain) | strongly chaotic (uncertain) | strongly chaotic (uncertain) |\n\n::: {.callout-note}\n**Interpretation Guide**\n\n- **Gain** = Increased complexity from normal to tumor\n- **Loss** = Complexity reduction from normal to tumor\n- **Chaotic** = Increased entropy from normal to tumor\n- **Anti-Chaotic** = Entropy reduction from normal to tumor\n- **P-values** = All p-values unadjusted unless noted\n:::\n\n:::\n\n### GO Biological Process Clusters\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n#### Complexity Change\n\n<h4>Gain Complexity Clusters</h4>\n<table class=\"table table-striped table-hover table-condensed\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th style=\"text-align:left;\"> Cluster </th>\n   <th style=\"text-align:right;\"> # Terms </th>\n   <t